{{project.category_list}}
Discovery:
- tool_search('keyword') -- find tools by keyword. No arguments lists every category.
- prompts/list -- index of skill packs (skill/*), per-category tool listings (domain/*), and named workflows (workflow/*). prompts/get with name=<entry> fetches one prompt.
- resources/list -- index of structured resources (claireon://tools/all, claireon://tools/{category}, claireon://blueprint/authoring-patterns, claireon://project/info, claireon://server/health). resources/read with uri=<uri> fetches one resource.

When you need domain knowledge (animation / GAS / progression / FS module architecture / build / debugging / testing / migration / code review / UI / Sample / coding conventions), pull skill/<area> via prompts/get instead of grepping the source tree. Use python_execute (the MCP tool) to run tool code.
